OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,FA man has admitted severely injuring a
OL,7,Fpolice officer by hitting him with a
OL,8,Fcar while driving recklessly in
OL,9,FDumfries.
OL,11,FInspector Jonathan Edgar, of Police
OL,12,FScotland, was thrown 10-15ft across
OL,13,Fthe road after he was struck by the
OL,14,Fvehicle driven by Martin McGroary,
OL,15,Ffrom Kilmarnock, on July 28 last year.
OL,17,FThe police officer was left with a
OL,18,Fdislocated shoulder and head and
OL,19,Ffacial injuries and has been unable to
OL,20,Freturn to work.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
