OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,FMcGroary, 27, of Kilmarnock, admitted
OL,7,Fdriving in a "culpable and reckless
OL,8,Fmanner" and at "excessive speed" and
OL,9,Fdriving knowing that Mr Edgar was on
OL,10,Fthe road before the collision on
OL,11,FHerries Avenue when he appeared at the
OL,12,FHigh Court in Glasgow on Wednesday.
OL,14,FHe also pleaded guilty to failing to
OL,15,Fstop and give his details after the
OL,16,Fcollision, and to driving without
OL,17,Finsurance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,FThe court heard that police were
OL,7,Fcalled to the street shortly after
OL,8,Fmidnight on July 28 by a resident who
OL,9,Fwas concerned about the presence of
OL,10,FMcGroary, whose brother had recently
OL,11,Fdied in a road crash.
OL,13,FSolicitor Advocate David Dickson KC,
OL,14,Fsaid officers then became "concerned"
OL,15,Fthat the accused was going to get out
OL,16,Fof the car as it was the third time he
OL,17,Fhad driven up and down the street.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,FThe prosecutor said: "The accused
OL,7,Fclosed the driver door and was then
OL,8,Fseen accelerating, driving towards
OL,9,Fboth police vehicles and where
OL,10,FInspector Edgar stood beside the
OL,11,Fvehicle.
OL,13,F"In an effort to avoid being struck,
OL,14,Fhe began to run across the road
OL,15,Ftowards the pavement."
OL,17,FMr Dickson told the court that,
OL,18,Fdespite his efforts, the policeman was
OL,19,Fstruck by the car and was thrown about
OL,20,F10-15ft across the road.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,FHe was taken to hospital where he was
OL,7,Ftreated for a dislocated shoulder and
OL,8,Fhead and facial injuries and was
OL,9,Fdischarged about 48 hours later.
OL,11,FThe court heard that he has been
OL,12,Funable to return to work.
OL,14,FMr McGroary will be sentenced on May
OL,15,F28 pending reports and remains
OL,16,Fremanded in custody.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Scott Wilson said:
OL,7,F"This was a terrifying incident for
OL,8,Fthe officer involved, who was left
OL,9,Fwith serious injuries as a result of
OL,10,FMcGroary's actions
OL,12,F"Following extensive inquiries and
OL,13,Fhard work by a dedicated team of
OL,14,Fofficers to trace McGroary, he was
OL,15,Fsubsequently arrested in connection
OL,16,Fwith the incident.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,F"I hope this conviction brings some
OL,7,Fcomfort to the officer and his
OL,8,Fcolleagues and sends a message that
OL,9,Fthis type of violent behaviour against
OL,10,Fpolice officers and staff will not be
OL,11,Ftolerated."
OL,13,FChief Inspector Emma Dodds said: "I
OL,14,Fwant to express my thanks and
OL,15,Fgratitude to those involved for their
OL,16,Fbravery and professionalism when faced
OL,17,Fwith such danger.
OL,19,F"Every officer has the fundamental
OL,20,Fright to come home from each shift
OL,21,Funharmed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777543610
OL,3,CMan admits severely injuring police
OL,4,Cofficer by hitting him with car
OL,6,F"This type of incident shows the
OL,7,Funpredictable and dangerous situations
OL,8,Fpolice officers can face, while doing
OL,9,Ftheir utmost to keep people safe."
